ed.getParams().getQ()).isEqualTo(q);\n        assertThat(deserialized.getParams().getG()).isEqualTo(g);\n        assertThat(deserialized.getEncoded()).isNotEmpty();\n        assertThat(deserialized.toString()).contains(\"DSA Public Key\", y.toString(16));\n    }\n\n    private static BCDSAPublicKey createPublicKey(BigInteger y, BigInteger p, BigInteger q, BigInteger g)\n        throws Exception {\n        DSAParameter dsaParameter = new DSAParameter(p, q, g);\n        AlgorithmIdentifier algorithmIdentifier = new AlgorithmIdentifier(\n            X9ObjectIdentifiers.id_dsa,\n            dsaParameter.toASN1Primitive());\n        SubjectPublicKeyInfo publicKeyInfo = new SubjectPublicKeyInfo(algorithmIdentifier, new ASN1Integer(y));\n        return new BCDSAPublicKey(publicKeyInfo);\n    }\n\n    private static byte[] serialize(Object value) throws Exception {\n        ByteArrayOutputStream bytes = new ByteArrayOutputStream();\n        try (ObjectOutputStream output = new ObjectOutputStream(bytes)) {\n            output.writeObject(value);\n        }\n        return bytes.toByteArray();\n    }\n\n    private static Object deserialize(byte[] value) throws Exception {\n        try (ObjectInputStream input = new ObjectInputStream(new ByteArrayInputStream(value))) {\n            return input.readObject();\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}
